"00:14.273" end="00:14.579">don</span> <span begin="00:14.579" end="00:14.935">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">说变没变 是啊 我已改变</span></p><p begin="00:14.935" end="00:17.910" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:14.935" end="00:15.264">Don</span> <span begin="00:15.264" end="00:15.665">me,</span> <span begin="00:15.665" end="00:16.033">called</span> <span begin="00:16.033" end="00:16.374">on</span> <span begin="00:16.374" end="00:16.807">me,</span> <span begin="00:16.807" end="00:17.244">called</span> <span begin="00:17.244" end="00:17.501">on</span> <span begin="00:17.501" end="00:17.910">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">变了 找上我 一遍一遍</span></p><p begin="00:17.910" end="00:20.918" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:17.910" end="00:18.249">Don</span> <span begin="00:18.249" end="00:18.676">me</span> <span begin="00:18.676" end="00:19.044">ain't</span> <span begin="00:19.044" end="00:19.378">don</span> <span begin="00:19.378" end="00:19.792">me</span> <span begin="00:19.792" end="00:20.196">yeah</span> <span begin="00:20.196" end="00:20.472">don</span> <span begin="00:20.472" end="00:20.918">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">说变没变 是啊 我已改变</span></p><p begin="00:20.918" end="00:23.850" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:20.918" end="00:21.207">Don</span> <span begin="00:21.207" end="00:21.661">me,</span> <span begin="00:21.661" end="00:22.048">called</span> <span begin="00:22.048" end="00:22.328">on</span> <span begin="00:22.328" end="00:22.764">me,</span> <span begin="00:22.764" end="00:23.161">called</span> <span begin="00:23.161" end="00:23.504">on</span> <span begin="00:23.504" end="00:23.850">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我变了 找上我 一遍一遍</span></p><p begin="00:24.580" end="00:28.324" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:24.580" end="00:25.008">Doing</span> <span begin="00:25.008" end="00:25.281">like</span> <span begin="00:26.070" end="00:26.818">95</span> <span begin="00:27.255" end="00:27.373">on</span> <span begin="00:27.373" end="00:27.559">the</span> <span begin="00:27.559" end="00:28.324">interstate</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">州际公路上开到九十五迈</span></p><p begin="00:28.324" end="00:29.827" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:28.324" end="00:28.715">Looking</span> <span begin="00:28.715" end="00:28.945">for</span> <span begin="00:28.945" end="00:29.086">a</span> <span begin="00:29.086" end="00:29.488">dinner</span> <span begin="00:29.488" end="00:29.827">plate</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只为找一口饭菜</span></p><p begin="00:30.502" end="00:32.783" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:30.502" end="00:30.577">I'm</span> <span begin="00:30.577" end="00:31.304">hungry,</span> <span begin="00:32.057" end="00:32.099">you</span> <span begin="00:32.099" end="00:32.499">called</span> <span begin="00:32.499" end="00:32.783">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我正饿着，你就打来</span></p><p begin="00:33.358" end="00:35.742" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:33.358" end="00:33.444">To</span> <span begin="00:33.444" end="00:33.815">say</span> <span begin="00:33.815" end="00:33.955">you</span> <span begin="00:33.955" end="00:34.145">got</span> <span begin="00:34.145" end="00:34.662">something,</span> <span begin="00:34.662" end="00:34.786">and</span> <span begin="00:34.786" end="00:35.004">it's</span> <span begin="00:35.004" end="00:35.383">all</span> <span begin="00:35.383" end="00:35.742">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">说你有货，全冲我来</span></p><p begin="00:36.516" end="00:41.826" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:36.516" end="00:36.874">Can</span> <span begin="00:36.874" end="00:37.211">you</span> <span begin="00:38.019" end="00:38.394">hold</span> <span begin="00:38.394" end="00:38.752">me</span> <span begin="00:38.987" end="00:39.333">down</span> <span begin="00:39.333" end="00:39.540">for</span> <span begin="00:39.540" end="00:39.893">one</span> <span begin="00:39.893" end="00:40.175">night,</span> <span begin="00:40.233" end="00:40.419">like</span> <span begin="00:40.419" end="00:40.607">I</span> <span begin="00:40.607" end="00:40.977">got</span> <span begin="00:40.977" end="00:41.208">three</span> <span begin="00:41.208" end="00:41.826">strikes?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">能不能陪我一整晚，就当我已经没有退路？</span></p><p begin="00:42.282" end="00:47.946" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:42.282" end="00:42.476">I</span> <span begin="00:42.476" end="00:42.856">need</span> <span begin="00:42.856" end="00:43.230">you</span> <span begin="00:43.772" end="00:43.882">to</span> <span begin="00:43.882" end="00:44.450">free</span> <span begin="00:44.450" end="00:44.733">me,</span> <span begin="00:45.830" end="00:46.050">it's</span> <span begin="00:46.050" end="00:46.188">a</span> <span begin="00:46.188" end="00:46.479">prison</span> <span begin="00:46.479" end="00:46.942">inside</span> <span begin="00:46.942" end="00:47.506">my</span> <span begin="00:47.506" end="00:47.946">mind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我需要你放我出来，我脑子里像是座监狱</span></p><p begin="00:48.466" end="00:50.697" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="00:48.466" end="00:48.813">Break</span> <span begin="00:48.813" end="00:49.145">me,</span> <span begin="00:49.965" end="00:50.404">taste</span> <span begin="00:50.404" end="00:50.697">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">击碎我，品尝我</span></p><p begin="00:51.805" end="00:54.077" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="00:51.805" end="00:51.972">Roll</span> <span begin="00:51.972" end="00:52.345">me</span> <span begin="00:52.345" end="00:52.540">up</span> <span begin="00:52.540" end="00:52.735">like</span> <span begin="00:52.735" end="00:52.910">the</span> <span begin="00:52.910" end="00:53.662">northern</span> <span begin="00:53.662" end="00:54.077">lights</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">把我卷起，像北极光一样燃着</span></p><p begin="00:54.420" end="00:59.612" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="00:54.420" end="00:54.776">Can</span> <span begin="00:54.776" end="00:55.099">you</span> <span begin="00:55.906" end="00:56.268">hold</span> <span begin="00:56.268" end="00:56.564">me</span> <span begin="00:56.889" end="00:57.221">down</span> <span begin="00:57.221" end="00:57.438">for</span> <span begin="00:57.438" end="00:57.735">one</span> <span begin="00:57.735" end="00:58.026">night,</span> <span begin="00:58.148" end="00:58.335">like</span> <span begin="00:58.335" end="00:58.532">I</span> <span begin="00:58.532" end="00:58.731">got</span> <span begin="00:58.897" end="00:59.167">three</span> <span begin="00:59.167" end="00:59.612">strikes?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">能不能陪我一整晚，就当我已经没有退路？</span></p><p begin="00:59.612" end="01:02.584" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="00:59.612" end="01:00.020">Don</span> <span begin="01:00.020" end="01:00.360">me</span> <span begin="01:00.360" end="01:00.732">ain't</span> <span begin="01:00.732" end="01:01.135">don</span> <span begin="01:01.135" end="01:01.487">me</span> <span begin="01:01.487" end="01:01.859">yeah</span> <span begin="01:01.859" end="01:02.278">don</span> <span begin="01:02.278" end="01:02.584">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">说变没变 是啊 我已改变</span></p><p begin="01:02.645" end="01:05.613" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:02.645" end="01:02.997">Don</span> <span begin="01:02.997" end="01:03.401">me,</span> <span begin="01:03.401" end="01:03.741">called</span> <span begin="01:03.741" end="01:04.112">on</span> <span begin="01:04.112" end="01:04.496">me,</span> <span begin="01:04.496" end="01:04.871">called</span> <span begin="01:04.871" end="01:05.265">on</span> <span begin="01:05.265" end="01:05.613">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我变了 找上我 一遍一遍</span></p><p begin="0